        "Description": "This presentation will cover the Black Arts of Cracks, KeyGens, Malware for the .NET Framework. The information in this presentation will show how a .NET programmer can do unspeakable things to .NET applications. I will cover the life cycle of developing such attacks and overcoming common countermeasures. - This presentation will focus on C# but applies to any application based on the .NET framework. - This presentation will focus on common application protections systems.",
