        "Description": "HTML5 isn't just video and canvas! There's a lot of clever related technology tucked away inside the mass of JavaScript specifications that aren't quite as sexy as a web socket making love to a canvas - but without a doubt, still useful and important to building web applications.This session will introduce you to some of those outliers, show you how they can be used and prepare you for making the most of what the browsers today can offer you.",
